      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-02-09/magnificent-or-marxist-passive-investing-is-back-on-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[指数基金不断在大型科技股中吹出看似更大的泡沫。以任何价格购买根本不是好的资本主义。]]></description>
